Anémone https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/An%C3%A9mone 0 Anémone (born Anne Bourguignon; born 9 August 1950) is a French actress, filmmaker and political activist. She took her stage name in 1968 from the title of her film debut in Philippe Garrel's "Anémone".
